name: First Alias-Free GAN Latent Space Walk - Painterly Faces
description:
This is my first latent space walk created with my version of Alias-Free GAN (based on rosinality’s unofficial implementation).

Trained on a custom dataset of painted portraits from many artists. Transfer learning off rosinality’s ffhq model.

[gif description: Short animation morphs between two stylized portraits. Both femme people with their eyes fixed perfectly as the the black hair of the first transitions into a blue gray of the second. There are diamond patterns, characteristic of an undertrained alias-free gan model.]

Tools used: custom code, google colab, imagemagick
